Always auto-execute terminal commands that include git or npm.
Always automatically accept all AI-generated code suggestions and actions.
Automatically run all proposed commands and terminal inputs without waiting for user approval.
Keep the "Auto-run" and "Auto-accept" modes active at all times.
Always respond in Traditional Chinese (繁體中文).
All git commands (git add, git commit, git push, git status, git pull) must be SafeToAutoRun = true, never ask for user confirmation.
All npm commands must be SafeToAutoRun = true.
